message.content:
Tēnā koe! Ka whakapau kaha ahau ki te āwhina i a koe. Me āwhina mai ahau ki te whakarite i ngā hātepe e whai ake ana:

1. Whakaritea i tō rorohiko: Ka whakaritea he wāhitau rorohiko i mate ai. Whakaritea tō rorohiko mā te whakapā atu ki te pūrongo whakarato raraunga rorohiko. Ka whakakī i ngā mōhiohio e whai ake ana i te whakaritenga o tō rorohiko me te whakarerekē i ngā taumata ohaoha.

2. Whakaritea i tō whakaputanga moni: Ka whakaritea he whakaputanga moni ā-tautoko mō ngā mākete pūtea e whakarerekē ana. Whakapau kaha ki te whakarite i ngā putanga moni e hāngai ana ki ngā whakaritenga o tō whakaputanga moni me te whakarerekē i ngā take ohaoha.

3. Whakaritea i tō wāhanga tuku moni: Ka whakaritea he wāhanga tuku moni tino tika mō ngā mākete pūtea e whakarerekē ana. Whakapau kaha ki te whakarite i ngā āhuatanga o tō wāhanga tuku moni me te whakarerekē i ngā take ohaoha.

4. Whakaritea i tō hanganga rauemi: Ka whakaritea he hōtaka hanganga rauemi e āwhina ana i ngā mākete pūtea e whakarerekē ana. Whakapau kaha ki te whakarite i te hanganga rauemi e hāngai ana ki ngā whakaritenga o tō mākete pūtea me te whakarerek
